&amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;&quot;&gt; (expressão) &lt;span class=&quot;SpellE&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;i style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-style:
